title: Rewards problem:::::: ?
body: Today i recieved the platinum trim on my summoner profile, but do not have plat border, or the victorious maokai skin (though i did recieve maokai) . Is there a problem? Should i be worried?

replies.body: There's no problem or anything wrong with your account.  Some players have also reported that one thing or another are missing, but we're not finished gifting rewards to every eligible player.  You may see that some content is still missing or that one player may have erceived them sooner than another, but don't worry!  Per the [Season 6 FAQ](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/page/2016-ranked-season-ends-soon), we aim to have this wrapped up by the 21st.  Hope that helps offer some ease!
It does, thank you for the quick response!
